        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">KNOB for parallel plays:</span> KNOB (10pts) is only 4 letters and starts with KN — perfect for creating parallel plays alongside existing words. The K and B create new crosswords easily.</p></div>
